body:
{{champion:44}} Any chance of easing his early mana costs or improving his heal value early on? Alternatively, adjustments to Righteous Glory to include armor and remove something else so he could viably build Catalyst would work. 

He absolutely struggles with the bot aggression and is a superior pick elsewhere so he can skip his terrible costs. I&#039;d love to hear some thoughts on him. {{champion:44}}

I should add that, making Catalyst a better purchase on him lategame would be fantastic, without having to buy items meant for AP carries that end up useless on him.
